snippet.title: SPEED DREAMS - 2.3.0 New Release Features
snippet.description:
Greetings friends, the Speed Dreams development team are very happy to bring you this new version 2.3.0.  Let's take a look  in this video at some of the main new features. The details of this release could be found here:
https://www.speed-dreams.net/en/new-2-3-0-release/

You can find this game and more info about this Open Source project on:
https://www.speed-dreams.net 

This video was created using KDENLIVE,  AVIDEMUX and GIMP

MUSIC: Severe Tire Damage
Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0 License
http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

The Speed Dreams Dev Team 2023

#OpenSource #SpeedDreams #SimRacing #NewRelease
